reviewText: We were looking for some patriotic music and pictures for a ladies banquet. This video was just what we hoped for - traditional patriotic music.
Watched the video instead of having the real fireworks this year, great to have!

This is a great purchase for beautiful scenery with nostalgic music to bring back many memories.  The residents at our assisted living home loved this on Memorial Day and complimented the music that went with the gorgeous scenery!  It was a hit!
